snippet.title: CO.AG Music
snippet.description:
Music Composer and producer, creating Space, Sci Fi, Ambient Dark Horror and Supernatural music using the latest Technology. Some are less than a minutes long and others are up to 60 minutes All the music is copyright and royalty free so feel free to use it for your presentations or projects. All I ask if you do wish to use any of my music is you credit me in your description and sent me a message at  Coagmusic@gmail.com or the CO.AG Facebook page  https://www.facebook.com/COAG-Music-146339785905623/  because I would love to see how they fit into your work. Thank you very much for subscribing to my channel.


If you would like to support me for the copyright free music I produce on this channel donations to my Paypal are very appreciated! 
paypal.me/AlanG286 

or you can support me on Patreon - https://www.patreon.com/user?ty=h&u=3550597

CO.AG Facebook page  https://www.facebook.com/COAG-Music-146339785905623/

Thanks for Listening, CO.AG.
